title: Ranks 1000-2500 in Pessat
content:
How many are attending the second round counseling?

comments.body: mention ur ranks as well pls( no doxx)
If you are trying to evaluate your chances of getting a particular branch through this poll, then i would say, just chill, you are taking way too much stress - just sit back and relax! :-)

For something which is not in your control - stop worrying about it.  
Remember, things don't get better by worrying about them :-)
okay I will try. btw do you know what happens to the pessat seat which gets converted to kcet? do they get added in second round or get converted to management?
There'll be a few seats reserved for lateral entry people. The remaining seats will become management seats. PES is definitely not gonna give seats for 1 lpa when they can get like 10-12 lpa
